This is the Voice Over Text for our video pitch. We want to translate it and then record it in different languages.

### Voiceover
Have you ever wondered why people fight for human rights?

Beyond Activismo collects histories of activists around the world. To be published on our website, based on 3 principles.

Openness.

Decentralization.

Digital Inclusion.

All our content is available in several languages.

Re-framing Activism is our way to make a change!
We believe that making visible the human side beyond it will empower not just Activist but others to take action in their communities.

Participate in our discussion.

Follow us on twitter.
